snippet.textDisplay:
"Any being who's had trauma wants to be loved and move forward. They don't want to be treated like they're damaged. and Tanja never treated her that way.

~ As a result they have moved forward with this beautiful life ~

How quickly we sometimes judge others and even ourselves for "being" stupid, strange, mean etc. Often not knowing how this person became so........ Still there is a story behind it and often a crie for help, a longing for change, for love! Yes for a beautiful life...

Truthful words I needed to hear.
